
Interfaces:

UNIX socket
    local authentication requests

    Protocol:
        Request: UNIX domain datagram containing the Yubikey one time password
        Response:

UDP Socket for counter synchronization
    Protocol:
        Notification:
            public_id
            counter
            hmac


Peers:
    ip_address
    shared_secret

Identities:
    public_id           CHAR(12)
    serial_number
    uid #private_id
    username
    aes_key
    counter
    last_valid_key


